name: Add Game Ball
description: This action is used to modify the (amount of) balls in the map

properties.name: BallArchetype
properties.description: Reference to the archetype of the ball to spawn

input.name: Add
input.description: Activating this input causes a ball to spawn

input.name: DestroyAll
input.description: Activating this input destroys all balls

output.name: Added
output.description: Activates when a ball has been spawned

output.name: Destroyed
output.description: Activates when a ball has been destroyed

output.name: DestroyedAll
output.description: Activates when all balls have been destroyed

variable.name: SpawnTransform
variable.description: Set the spawn location of the ball

name: Display Message
description: This actions is used to show the player a message with a title and description. If enabled, two buttons are shown

properties.name: bShowButtonOne
properties.description: If checked, the first button will be shown

properties.name: bShowButtonTwo
properties.description: If checked, the second button will be shown

properties.name: ButtonOneTitle
properties.description: The text for the first button

properties.name: ButtonTwoTitle
properties.description: The text for the second button

input.name: Set
input.description: Activating this input causes the message to show

output.name: Button One Clicked
output.description: Activates when the player clickes the first button

output.name: Button Two Clicked
output.description: Activates when the player clickes the second button

name: Is Target In Player Camera View
Set Scalar Parameter on Static Meshes
